overview: Clash of Champions (2016) is an upcoming professional wrestling pay-per-view event and WWE Network event produced by WWE. It will take place on September 25, 2016 at the Bankers Life Fieldhouse in Indianapolis, Indiana. It will be the first WWE event under the Clash of Champions chronology, replacing Night of Champions. It will also be the first Raw branded event following the second WWE brand extension in July 2016.
title: WWE Clash of Champions 2016
